g.text: Website​Evaluation​Worksheet​Use this form to evaluate each of the web sites for your topic.​For help evaluating the websites visit:​http://lib.berkeley.edu/TeachingLib/Guides/Internet/Evaluate.html

svg.text: Evaluation Questions​Is there an author listed? If so, who is it?
Is this site affiliated with an organization, company, institution or agency? If​yes, which one and is it a reputable organization?
